{
  "page": "Lies of the Ancients",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Lies of the Ancients</b></i> is a work by <a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">Archmaester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Fomas\" title=\"Fomas\">Fomas</a>. It is little regarded due to its erroneous claims regarding the founding of <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyria</a> and certain lineal claims in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. It also speculates that the mythic <a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a> were nothing more than a tribe of <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> established on the far north and forced by the <a href=\"/index.php/Long_Night\" title=\"Long Night\">Long Night</a> to engage in conquests to the south, becoming monstrous in tales told thereafter by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> to give themselves a heroic background as saviors of mankind.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lies_of_the_Ancients&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_long_night.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Long Night.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404232338\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.022 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.047 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 101/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8555/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 343/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 93/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 571/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   42.616      1 -total\n 84.09%   35.835      1 Template:Italic_title\n 11.93%    5.082      1 Template:Ref\n  7.37%    3.141      1 Template:Ref/core\n  3.46%    1.475      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18577-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404232338 and revision id 239325\n -->\n",
